# Flutter/Dart/Pub related
**/doc/api/
**/ios/Flutter/.last_build_id
.dart_tool/
.flutter-plugins
.flutter-plugins-dependencies
.pub-cache/
.pub/
/build/
/coverage/

# NOTE: pubspec.lock is intentionally NOT ignored for applications —
# it must stay in version control so `flutter pub get` reproduces the
# exact same dependency versions the app was built and tested with.

# Symbolication related
app.*.symbols

# Obfuscation related
app.*.map.json

